Package: IPTM
Title: Interaction-Partitioned Topic Models
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Bomin", "Kim", email = "bzk147@psu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Jones", "Zachary", email = "zmj@zmjones.com", role = c("aut", "adp")))
URL: https://github.com/bomin8319/IPTM
BugReports: https://github.com/bomin8319/IPTM/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Description: Functions jointly analyze the history of interaction (between the sender and receiver) and 
             the contents or topic of text (e.g. email, online messages) using Markov chain Monte Carlo (MCMC). 
